OL,3,CAs record-breaking heatwave continues,
OL,4,Chow likely are further wildfires?
OL,6,FBy Producer Anthony France
OL,8,FFirefighters in Derbyshire are
OL,9,Fbattling a 500 square metre wildfire
OL,10,Fon Tintwistle Moor, with dramatic
OL,11,Fdrone footage showing smoke billowing
OL,12,Finto the sky and flames consuming
OL,13,Ftrees.
OL,15,FLocal residents are being urged to
OL,16,Fkeep their windows and doors firmly
OL,17,Fshut near Glossop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
