OL,3,CAs record-breaking heatwave continues,
OL,4,Chow likely are further wildfires?
OL,6,FProfessor Friederike Otto, professor
OL,7,Fof climate science at Imperial College
OL,8,FLondon, said: "Scientists like me are
OL,9,Fbeginning to sound like a broken
OL,10,Frecord.
OL,12,F"Yes this is climate change, yes it's
OL,13,Fus, no it's not El Nino, yes we have
OL,14,Fthe solutions, no we're not
OL,15,Fimplementing them fast enough.
OL,17,F"It's really now a question of what
OL,18,Fkind of future we want for ourselves,
OL,19,Fand whether we're willing to do what
OL,20,Fit takes to secure it."
OL,26,@pD@OOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
