OL,3,CAs record-breaking heatwave continues,
OL,4,Chow likely are further wildfires?
OL,6,FThe Fylingdales Moor wildfire ravaged
OL,7,Fthousands of hectares of precious
OL,8,Fmoorland and peatland in North
OL,9,FYorkshire last summer.
OL,11,FIn the 40.2C summer of July 2022,
OL,12,Fscores of homes were destroyed by
OL,13,Ffires in the village of Wennington,
OL,14,Fnear Rainham, and Dagenham in east
OL,15,FLondon.
OL,17,FFire crews had their busiest 24 hours
OL,18,Fsince the Second World War tackling
OL,19,Fmore than 200 blazes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
