OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782544686
OL,3,CAs record-breaking heatwave continues,
OL,4,Chow likely are further wildfires?
OL,6,FAccording to the RSPB in May 2023, a
OL,7,FScottish wildfire thought to be the
OL,8,FUK's largest at the time destroyed 25
OL,9,Fyears of recreating and restoring
OL,10,Fhabitats of wildlife such as Black
OL,11,FGrouse and Scottish Crossbill near
OL,12,FCannich in the Highlands.
OL,14,FIts 12-mile plume of smoke was
OL,15,Fdetected from space by Nasa satellites.
OL,17,FAnother wildfire in the same month saw
OL,18,Fa vital habitat at Lady Cannings
OL,19,FPlantation near Burbage Moor,
OL,20,FSheffield go up in smoke.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
