OL,3,CAs record-breaking heatwave continues,
OL,4,Chow likely are further wildfires?
OL,6,FHow can we prevent wildfires?
OL,8,FLondon Fire Brigade (LFB) Deputy
OL,9,FCommissioner Spencer Sutcliff issued
OL,10,Fcouncils and landowners with a warning
OL,11,Fon the increased risk of devastating
OL,12,Fwildfires by asking those responsible
OL,13,Ffor managing green spaces to create
OL,14,Ffire breaks to help protect lives and
OL,15,Fproperties.
OL,17,FThis includes cutting long dry grass
OL,18,For ploughing earth to remove any
OL,19,Fflammable vegetation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782544686
OL,3,CAs record-breaking heatwave continues,
OL,4,Chow likely are further wildfires?
OL,6,FBarriers prevent the rapid spread of
OL,7,Fflames by reducing or eliminating the
OL,8,Ffuel available for wildfires.
OL,10,FAlso advised is avoiding the use of
OL,11,Fdisposable barbecues or campfires in
OL,12,Fparks and open spaces, ensuring
OL,13,Fcigarettes are put out completely and
OL,14,Fdisposed of correctly, as well as
OL,15,Ftaking rubbish home if no bins are
OL,16,Favailable.
OL,18,FHomeowners can also help by
OL,19,Fmaintaining their gardens by
OL,20,Fpreventing them becoming overgrown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782544686
OL,3,CAs record-breaking heatwave continues,
OL,4,Chow likely are further wildfires?
OL,6,FLast year, London experienced its
OL,7,Fhighest number of wildfires since the
OL,8,Fextreme heat of 2022, LFB said.
OL,10,FFirefighters attended around 83 across
OL,11,Fthe capital during June, July and
OL,12,FAugust.
OL,14,FWhat is the government doing about
OL,15,Fwildfires?
OL,17,FNearly #100 million is being invested
OL,18,Fin specialist firefighters and an
OL,19,Foverhaul of fire and rescue equipment
OL,20,Fto tackle the growing risk of
OL,21,Fwildfires.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782544686
OL,3,CAs record-breaking heatwave continues,
OL,4,Chow likely are further wildfires?
OL,6,FThe teams who have state-of-the-art
OL,7,Fkit and dedicated off-road vehicles
OL,8,Fwill be positioned in key areas across
OL,9,FLancashire, Greater Manchester,
OL,10,FNorthumberland, London and South Wales
OL,11,Ffrom the end of June.
OL,13,FThe Ministry of Housing, Communities
OL,14,Fand Local Government said they would
OL,15,Fhelp people on the ground more quickly
OL,16,Fand ease the pressure on local
OL,17,Fservices.
OL,19,FOfficers travelled to South Africa and
OL,20,FPoland to learn from international
OL,21,Fcounterparts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
