OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782544686
OL,3,CAs record-breaking heatwave continues,
OL,4,Chow likely are further wildfires?
OL,6,FThe #97m boost also includes the
OL,7,Fbiggest upgrade to National Resilience
OL,8,Ffire vehicles and equipment in 20
OL,9,Fyears, the MHCLG said.
OL,11,FThe National Resilience programme was
OL,12,Festablished after the 9/11 attacks and
OL,13,Fprovides specialist capabilities,
OL,14,Fstaff and resources for special
OL,15,Fincidents including natural disasters,
OL,16,Findustrial accidents or terrorist
OL,17,Fattacks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
