PN,30817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782544686
OL,3,CAs record-breaking heatwave continues,
OL,4,Chow likely are further wildfires?
OL,6,FBuilding safety minister Samantha
OL,7,FDixon said: "This country benefits
OL,8,Ffrom a dedicated fire and rescue
OL,9,Fservice and as incidents continue to
OL,10,Fevolve in complexity, it's critical
OL,11,Fthat we back those on the frontline
OL,12,Fwith the latest equipment.
OL,14,F"Last year saw some of our most
OL,15,Fdevastating wildfires in recent
OL,16,Fhistory and as we head into peak
OL,17,Fseason, we're getting on and
OL,18,Fdelivering the resource, training and
OL,19,Fassets needed to minimise the
OL,20,Fescalating risk."
OL,26,@oD@MOUvD@AOU|D@QO]
